{"tid":990784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【同Bob床上肉搏】為王祖藍一句話豁出去 吊帶蝦頭好「胸狠」","createTime":"2019-01-22T01:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T16:34:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"91f9fa2414ce58334f3d57bbbefb2d655adf8780","tid":990784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:32:32.000Z","msg":"王祖藍首次執導賀歲片《你咪理，我愛你！》，搵嚟唔少圈中好友幫手，好似楊詩敏（蝦頭）咁，呢套係佢加盟邵氏嘅第一套電影，戲中蝦頭同林盛斌（Bob）嘅床上肉搏戲，火辣紅色吊帶內衣上陣嘅蝦頭勁「胸狠」，相信觀眾們從未未見過佢如此性感過，蝦頭笑言因為導演祖藍一句：「阿蝦！豁出去啦！」，佢就好聽話咁豁咗出去，仲話當時祖藍見到都嚇咗一嚇！<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190120/large/1547973153_78b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547973153_78b2.jpg&h=5838c131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190120/large/1547965098_1736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547965098_1736.jpg&h=00155cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190120/large/1547965150_7aed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547965150_7aed.jpg&h=83ec3552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190120/large/1547965152_383c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547965152_383c.jpg&h=1de56ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190120/large/1547965153_e7d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547965153_e7d5.jpg&h=24092c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190120/large/1547965158_3eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimag